### Git-Ignore Setup
# Ignore everything
*

# Keep directories traversable so exceptions can work
!*/

# Keep Jupyter notebooks anywhere in the repo
!*.ipynb
!*.md

# Keep the ignore file itself tracked
!.gitignore

